      "content": "but it's not just being lost. it's like... i'm just taking up space. the art was the only thing that made the breathing part worth it, you know? without it, the \"me\" part is just dead weight. i'm just a biological machine running on autopilot, but the soul is just gone. it feels so heavy to just exist like this.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
